title: I still don't have the Hallowen icon
body: it's been more than two weeks and i still don't have the icon from "The teemoing".

replies.body: Shoot, sorry we missed you, bud! If you write a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) in, we'll be able to assist you with this icon. ^.^
